- Array(T)
- Date
- DateTime
- Enum8, Enum16
- FixedString(N)
- Float32, Float64
- Nullable(T)
- String
- Tuple
- UInt8, UInt16, UInt32, UInt64, Int8, Int16, Int32, Int64

